";
CM_ BO_ 2499798019 "All not used bits must be set at 1. Cycle time must be finalized (default value = 10 ms)";
CM_ SG_ 2499798019 Hrtbt "Init Value 251; The transmitter will increase the counter in every cycle,  0 to 250 and then wrap.254 Error; 255 NA. Approach Unilateral";
CM_ SG_ 2499798019 MsgChksum_4 "Chksum = (Byte1 + (Byte2 & 0x0F) + Byte3 + Byte4 + Byte5 + Byte6 + Byte7 + Bytes8 + msgID byte1 + msgID byte2 + msgID byte3 + msgID byte4)  = (((chksum >> 6) & 0x03) + (chksum >>3) + chksum) & 0x07 = ((chksum & 0x0F) << 4) + (chksum & 0x0F)";
CM_ SG_ 2499798019 SpecialModeResp "Not used on CH26. Setup with a value !=1 by all the other ECU that is receiving the Rqst information, on the WL SFB and maybe UCM";
