CM_ SG_ 2566870050 MsgCnt_EHR "Initial Value 12. Counts from 0 to 11 and then back to 0. 12, 13 are reserved, 14 error, 15 NA. Tecnord EHR Only";
CM_ SG_ 2566870050 EHR_FailSafe "The aim of this function is if an internal fault is detected by the valve, then the valve will default to either neutral or float depending on failsave mode set in the Ehr control message.";
