CM_ SG_ 2566870050 EHR_DynRmpTime "By using time ramps, the dynamics of the valve can be reduced in a well-targeted manner. The time ramp is the time required until the full stroke has been completed (from 0 to 100 % or from 100 to 0 % raising or lowering).";
